More general VarDict low frequency filters

VarDict low frequency linear filters tended to over filter on high depth panels
with strand bias and closely spaced mutations. This validates a
re-worked version that uses a cutoff based approach to remove most of
the same variants without over filtering on the cross validation
datasets.
